      "sentence_index": 4,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_37",
        "p4__w_38",
        "p4__w_39",
        "p4__w_40",
        "p4__w_41",
        "p4__w_42",
        "p4__w_43",
        "p4__w_44",
        "p4__w_45",
        "p4__w_46",
        "p4__w_47",
        "p4__w_48",
        "p4__w_49",
        "p4__w_50",
        "p4__w_51",
        "p4__w_52",
        "p4__w_53",
        "p4__w_54",
        "p4__w_55",
        "p4__w_56",
        "p4__w_57",
        "p4__w_58",
        "p4__w_59",
        "p4__w_60",
        "p4__w_61",
        "p4__w_62",
        "p4__w_63",
        "p4__w_64",
        "p4__w_65"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_5",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了4楼，电梯又停，我面露惊讶；到了5楼再停，我面露难过，汗水直流。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_66",
        "p4__w_67",
        "p4__w_68",
        "p4__w_69",
        "p4__w_70",
        "p4__w_71",
        "p4__w_72",
        "p4__w_73",
        "p4__w_74",
        "p4__w_75",
        "p4__w_76",
        "p4__w_77",
        "p4__w_78",
        "p4__w_79",
        "p4__w_80",
        "p4__w_81",
        "p4__w_82",
        "p4__w_83",
        "p4__w_84",
        "p4__w_85",
        "p4__w_86",
        "p4__w_87",
        "p4__w_88",
        "p4__w_89",
        "p4__w_90"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_6",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "电梯一路停靠，我从生气变为愤怒，最终濒临崩溃。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_91",
        "p4__w_92",
        "p4__w_93",
        "p4__w_94",
        "p4__w_95",
        "p4__w_96",
        "p4__w_97",
        "p4__w_98",
        "p4__w_99",
        "p4__w_100",
        "p4__w_101",
        "p4__w_102",
        "p4__w_103",
        "p4__w_104"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_7",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了87楼，电梯再次停下，我面露怒色，有人走进电梯，电梯反复开关，上上下下！",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_105",
        "p4__w_106",
        "p4__w_107",
        "p4__w_108",
        "p4__w_109",
        "p4__w_110",
        "p4__w_111",
        "p4__w_112",
        "p4__w_113",
        "p4__w_114",
        "p4__w_115",
        "p4__w_116",
        "p4__w_117",
        "p4__w_118",
        "p4__w_119",
        "p4__w_120",
        "p4__w_121",
        "p4__w_122",
        "p4__w_123",
        "p4__w_124",
        "p4__w_125",
        "p4__w_126"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_8",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我按下关门键，再按！",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_127",
        "p4__w_128",
        "p4__w_129",
        "p4__w_130",
        "p4__w_131",
        "p4__w_132",
        "p4__w_133",
        "p4__w_134"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_9",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "广播响起：“电梯限乘10人！超过10人禁止运行！”",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_135",
        "p4__w_136",
        "p4__w_137",
        "p4__w_138",
        "p4__w_139",
        "p4__w_140",
        "p4__w_141",
        "p4__w_142",
        "p4__w_143",
        "p4__w_144",
        "p4__w_145",
        "p4__w_146",
        "p4__w_147",
        "p4__w_148",
        "p4__w_149",
        "p4__w_150"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_10",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着电梯，面露烦躁。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_151",
        "p4__w_152",
        "p4__w_153",
        "p4__w_154",
        "p4__w_155",
        "p4__w_156",
        "p4__w_157"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_11",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看着挤在电梯里的人群，人数堪比木乃伊方阵，我面露怒色。",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_158",
        "p4__w_159",
        "p4__w_160",
        "p4__w_161",
        "p4__w_162",
        "p4__w_163",
        "p4__w_164",
        "p4__w_165",
        "p4__w_166",
        "p4__w_167",
        "p4__w_168",
        "p4__w_169",
        "p4__w_170",
        "p4__w_171",
        "p4__w_172",
        "p4__w_173"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p4__s_12",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "有人指着电梯门，示意里面的人不要出去，我彻底愤怒了！",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "children": [
        "p4__w_174",
        "p4__w_175",
        "p4__w_176",
        "p4__w_177",
        "p4__w_178",
        "p4__w_179",
        "p4__w_180",
        "p4__w_181",
        "p4__w_182",
        "p4__w_183",
        "p4__w_184",
        "p4__w_185",
        "p4__w_186",
        "p4__w_187",
        "p4__w_188",
        "p4__w_189"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_1",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时间到了！",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_1",
        "p5__w_2",
        "p5__w_3",
        "p5__w_4"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_2",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走进电梯，开门，快步前行，直行，下楼，再直行，上楼，折返，又下楼，再直行。",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_5",
        "p5__w_6",
        "p5__w_7",
        "p5__w_8",
        "p5__w_9",
        "p5__w_10",
        "p5__w_11",
        "p5__w_12",
        "p5__w_13",
        "p5__w_14",
        "p5__w_15",
        "p5__w_16",
        "p5__w_17",
        "p5__w_18",
        "p5__w_19",
        "p5__w_20",
        "p5__w_21",
        "p5__w_22",
        "p5__w_23",
        "p5__w_24",
        "p5__w_25",
        "p5__w_26",
        "p5__w_27",
        "p5__w_28",
        "p5__w_29",
        "p5__w_30"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_3",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了88楼，我继续前行，上楼，折返，下楼，再走，到了89楼！",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_31",
        "p5__w_32",
        "p5__w_33",
        "p5__w_34",
        "p5__w_35",
        "p5__w_36",
        "p5__w_37",
        "p5__w_38",
        "p5__w_39",
        "p5__w_40",
        "p5__w_41",
        "p5__w_42",
        "p5__w_43",
        "p5__w_44",
        "p5__w_45",
        "p5__w_46",
        "p5__w_47",
        "p5__w_48",
        "p5__w_49",
        "p5__w_50",
        "p5__w_51"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_4",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我快步跑进电梯。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_52",
        "p5__w_53",
        "p5__w_54",
        "p5__w_55",
        "p5__w_56"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_5",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我下楼、直行、再直行，转弯，突然弯腰咳嗽，缓过来后继续直行、转弯、再直行。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_57",
        "p5__w_58",
        "p5__w_59",
        "p5__w_60",
        "p5__w_61",
        "p5__w_62",
        "p5__w_63",
        "p5__w_64",
        "p5__w_65",
        "p5__w_66",
        "p5__w_67",
        "p5__w_68",
        "p5__w_69",
        "p5__w_70",
        "p5__w_71",
        "p5__w_72",
        "p5__w_73",
        "p5__w_74",
        "p5__w_75",
        "p5__w_76",
        "p5__w_77",
        "p5__w_78",
        "p5__w_79",
        "p5__w_80"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_6",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我刷工牌、用手机开门，一路快步走，一边挥手打招呼，再挥手，和一位女士道别。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_81",
        "p5__w_82",
        "p5__w_83",
        "p5__w_84",
        "p5__w_85",
        "p5__w_86",
        "p5__w_87",
        "p5__w_88",
        "p5__w_89",
        "p5__w_90",
        "p5__w_91",
        "p5__w_92",
        "p5__w_93",
        "p5__w_94",
        "p5__w_95",
        "p5__w_96",
        "p5__w_97",
        "p5__w_98",
        "p5__w_99",
        "p5__w_100",
        "p5__w_101",
        "p5__w_102",
        "p5__w_103",
        "p5__w_104"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_7",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我转弯、直行、开门、走到办公桌前坐下。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_105",
        "p5__w_106",
        "p5__w_107",
        "p5__w_108",
        "p5__w_109",
        "p5__w_110",
        "p5__w_111",
        "p5__w_112",
        "p5__w_113",
        "p5__w_114",
        "p5__w_115",
        "p5__w_116"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_8",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看着时钟，我额头冒汗。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_117",
        "p5__w_118",
        "p5__w_119",
        "p5__w_120",
        "p5__w_121",
        "p5__w_122",
        "p5__w_123"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p5__s_p5_9",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "做出胜利的手势！",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "children": [
        "p5__w_123",
        "p5__w_124",
        "p5__w_125",
        "p5__w_126",
        "p5__w_127"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_1",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "晚上九点，我接到了刚失恋的老友的电话，他让我过去陪他喝酒。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_001",
        "p21__w_002",
        "p21__w_003",
        "p21__w_004",
        "p21__w_005",
        "p21__w_006",
        "p21__w_007",
        "p21__w_008",
        "p21__w_009",
        "p21__w_010",
        "p21__w_011",
        "p21__w_012",
        "p21__w_013",
        "p21__w_014",
        "p21__w_015",
        "p21__w_016",
        "p21__w_017",
        "p21__w_018",
        "p21__w_019",
        "p21__w_020",
        "p21__w_021"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_2",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我本想开车过去，但路上堵车非常严重，到处都是车，还遇到了红灯和车祸。",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_022",
        "p21__w_023",
        "p21__w_024",
        "p21__w_025",
        "p21__w_026",
        "p21__w_027",
        "p21__w_028",
        "p21__w_029",
        "p21__w_030",
        "p21__w_031",
        "p21__w_032",
        "p21__w_033",
        "p21__w_034",
        "p21__w_035",
        "p21__w_036",
        "p21__w_037",
        "p21__w_038",
        "p21__w_039",
        "p21__w_040",
        "p21__w_041",
        "p21__w_042",
        "p21__w_043",
        "p21__w_044",
        "p21__w_045"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_3",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我只能无奈地在车里等待，心里非常着急。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_046",
        "p21__w_047",
        "p21__w_048",
        "p21__w_049",
        "p21__w_050",
        "p21__w_051",
        "p21__w_052",
        "p21__w_053",
        "p21__w_054",
        "p21__w_055",
        "p21__w_056",
        "p21__w_057",
        "p21__w_058"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_4",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "好不容易回到家，我开始喝酒。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_059",
        "p21__w_060",
        "p21__w_061",
        "p21__w_062",
        "p21__w_063",
        "p21__w_064",
        "p21__w_065",
        "p21__w_066"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_5",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "不久，老友也来了，他告诉我他失恋了，心里很难过。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_067",
        "p21__w_068",
        "p21__w_069",
        "p21__w_070",
        "p21__w_071",
        "p21__w_072",
        "p21__w_073",
        "p21__w_074",
        "p21__w_075",
        "p21__w_076",
        "p21__w_077",
        "p21__w_078",
        "p21__w_079",
        "p21__w_080",
        "p21__w_081",
        "p21__w_082",
        "p21__w_083",
        "p21__w_084"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_6",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我笑着安慰他，劝他不要再想那些不开心的事。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_085",
        "p21__w_086",
        "p21__w_087",
        "p21__w_088",
        "p21__w_089",
        "p21__w_090",
        "p21__w_091",
        "p21__w_092",
        "p21__w_093",
        "p21__w_094",
        "p21__w_095",
        "p21__w_096",
        "p21__w_097",
        "p21__w_098",
        "p21__w_099",
        "p21__w_100"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_7",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们一起喝酒，时间慢慢流逝。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_101",
        "p21__w_102",
        "p21__w_103",
        "p21__w_104",
        "p21__w_105",
        "p21__w_106",
        "p21__w_107",
        "p21__w_108"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_8",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "后来，老友要坐公交车回家，外面下起了雨。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_109",
        "p21__w_110",
        "p21__w_111",
        "p21__w_112",
        "p21__w_113",
        "p21__w_114",
        "p21__w_115",
        "p21__w_116",
        "p21__w_117",
        "p21__w_118",
        "p21__w_119",
        "p21__w_120",
        "p21__w_121"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_9",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我在楼下等他，他问我是不是和那个女人分手了，是不是坐公交车。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_122",
        "p21__w_123",
        "p21__w_124",
        "p21__w_125",
        "p21__w_126",
        "p21__w_127",
        "p21__w_128",
        "p21__w_129",
        "p21__w_130",
        "p21__w_131",
        "p21__w_132",
        "p21__w_133",
        "p21__w_134",
        "p21__w_135",
        "p21__w_136",
        "p21__w_137",
        "p21__w_138",
        "p21__w_139",
        "p21__w_140",
        "p21__w_141"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_10",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我告诉他是的，并且指向了天上的乌云。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_142",
        "p21__w_143",
        "p21__w_144",
        "p21__w_145",
        "p21__w_146",
        "p21__w_147",
        "p21__w_148",
        "p21__w_149",
        "p21__w_150",
        "p21__w_151",
        "p21__w_152",
        "p21__w_153"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_11",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "他说下雨了，没有太阳，还问我要不要伞。",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_154",
        "p21__w_155",
        "p21__w_156",
        "p21__w_157",
        "p21__w_158",
        "p21__w_159",
        "p21__w_160",
        "p21__w_161",
        "p21__w_162",
        "p21__w_163",
        "p21__w_164",
        "p21__w_165",
        "p21__w_166",
        "p21__w_167"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_12",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我同意了。",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_168",
        "p21__w_169",
        "p21__w_170",
        "p21__w_171"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_13",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们在雨中等待公交车，他去了趟卫生间。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_172",
        "p21__w_173",
        "p21__w_174",
        "p21__w_175",
        "p21__w_176",
        "p21__w_177",
        "p21__w_178",
        "p21__w_179",
        "p21__w_180",
        "p21__w_181",
        "p21__w_182",
        "p21__w_183"
      ]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "p21__s_21_14",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "等了很久，他终于出来了，还亲了我一下。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "children": [
        "p21__w_184",
        "p21__w_185",
        "p21__w_186",
        "p21__w_187",
